{"tid":1785583,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"從前有兩個儒生猜燈謎","createTime":"2019-12-16T13:13:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-17T13:17:36.000Z","uid":64232,"like":228,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"6a58f5e67f2511d6fc533f7dd8d11a5fa0586407","tid":1785583,"uid":64232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:13:48.000Z","msg":"正值月圓中秋之夜，二儒生經夜市而過，見一檔猜燈謎：<br />\n<br />\n謎題：<br />\n「提示：監。<br />\n閹割之物，有監之名無監之實，為伺候皇族而生。。」<br />\n<br />\n一人曰：「易如反掌，必為太監也！」<br />\n<br />\n「非也。」<br />\n<br />\n「閣下另有高見？」<br />\n<br />\n「監警會。」<br />\n<br />\n其人啞口無言。"},{"pid":"e62a561709622b391a8bbab53138cfe6844d8bd9","tid":1785583,"uid":64232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dd70e1ae54cd0309b6f19b1fc5f98426399b97f","tid":1785583,"uid":18170,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:14:13.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"ba11e127179157c4951e771197853c519189dd87","tid":1785583,"uid":64232,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:14:45.000Z","msg":"二儒又經一檔，見燈謎為：<br />\n<br />\n「猜一人。<br />\n設嚴苛律法，身受其害，作法自斃。」<br />\n<br />\n「商君衛鞅也。」<br />\n<br />\n「然，但答以刑部尚書鄭氏婦更為上品。」"},{"pid":"d31a0457f9759b1e0e82b435c0991c0106cfbe9e","tid":1785583,"uid":64232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:16:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d0f3801d97936919b54651b802bff430236f71c","tid":1785583,"uid":64232,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:16:46.000Z","msg":"問：哪一個城市可以沒有金融機構而成為金融中心？<br />\n<br />\n答：澳門。"},{"pid":"ba1f6adfceeaf574752fb980e72a28dc68dbc1d5","tid":1785583,"uid":64232,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T13:16:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49239cdf8bded7988dccccc85d155fdb77971117","tid